products.name: MASJID SULTAN
products.description: This exquisite watercolor painting captures the Sultan Mosque, a revered landmark in Singapore's Kampong Glam neighborhood. Highlighted by its striking golden dome, the mosque's grandeur is beautifully rendered against a backdrop of lush trees and a clear sky. The vibrant colors and soft brush strokes evoke a sense of tranquility and reverence. Prominently featured is the "Kandahar St" sign, situating the mosque within its vibrant community. This artwork is not only a celebration of the mosque's architectural beauty but also a testament to its role as a cornerstone of cultural heritage in Singapore.
